{"tid":1560251,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有關Supper Moment 一事]","createTime":"2019-09-11T06:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T14:00:26.000Z","uid":261741,"like":7,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9027c0002e23ca7d6e8d5e5547226eb9ffd2e6","tid":1560251,"uid":261741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:37:19.000Z","msg":"我有啲說話想講！<br />\n做乜鳩？點解死都要拉埋人落水？<br />\n唔通人地有出黎遊行又要逐個逐個通知聲？<br />\n有啲嘢就在心中啦，我唔可以擔保佢地四個都係撐我們，我真係唔知。但係佢地唔表態唔代表唔支持。<br />\n人哋有撚哂計劃去做演唱會，你們又屌。<br />\n人哋為咗台灣歌迷而去出專輯，去埋台灣宣傳，你們又屌。<br />\n人哋私底下出嚟遊行，轉個頭去搞演唱會，你們又屌佢地拎光環。<br />\n咁你地想點吖？<br />\n人哋一早講過唔會將政治同音樂一齊講，你們就死逼人哋去牆角。<br />\n咁撚有時間做啲抹黑人既事，不如揾時間搞下文宣，準備一下星期五上山。<br />\n人哋會唱無盡並不是錯，每個人吸收到嘅感受都唔同。<br />\n咪撚咁小題大做，咁敏感得唔得？<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<strong>光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n香港人，加油！</strong>"},{"pid":"b4de878e929e634570d46446a054df4e7c8519c1","tid":1560251,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:38:30.000Z","msg":"原來死線係10月1號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560249</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"da2b3d10505e10c43db9f1d4998a4b9ab4b3920b","tid":1560251,"uid":278404,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:45:57.000Z","msg":"「唔表態唔代表唔支持」<br />\n此post已完<br />\n<br />\n大是大非選擇沉默，咁叫唔表態？有冇見過維權政權嘅band仔？<br />\nRubberBand做到，點解濕爬做唔到？<br />\n<br />\n利申多年濕爬fans好心痛，準備轉會ekids"},{"pid":"4fe7d2161a94e5df3419ecaf6f6ef804d1b5ad81","tid":1560251,"uid":43304,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:53:30.000Z","msg":"負評不推文<br />\n收撚皮"},{"pid":"c7445ab080ed06f5615dccb91fd18542523e6db8","tid":1560251,"uid":173814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da2b3d10505e10c43db9f1d4998a4b9ab4b3920b","tid":1560251,"uid":278404,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:45:57.000Z","msg":"「唔表態唔代表唔支持」<br />\n此post已完<br />\n<br />\n大是大非選擇沉默，咁叫唔表態？有冇見過維權政權嘅band仔？<br />\nRubberBand做到，點解濕爬做唔到？<br />\n<br />\n利申多年濕爬fans好心痛，準備轉會ekids"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:48:23.000Z","msg":"轉KOLOR啦!"},{"pid":"c049ad2c6459f907e96b76cf58cd83b8d34a487e","tid":1560251,"uid":195650,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:26:30.000Z","msg":"唔係無表態<br />\n係表極都好似有人唔滿意<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tsRHYwN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtsRHYwN.png&h=8dc17faa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"431c530640a7f5b5c02aa756ecf0d57303655be9","tid":1560251,"uid":195650,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:28:18.000Z","msg":"講極都嫌唔夠明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Rbpsqy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Rbpsqy.png&h=e5b09c41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7801dbccd7f328fec84e3d5029fdfbb03784d4bd","tid":1560251,"uid":186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c049ad2c6459f907e96b76cf58cd83b8d34a487e","tid":1560251,"uid":195650,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:26:30.000Z","msg":"唔係無表態<br />\n係表極都好似有人唔滿意<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tsRHYwN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtsRHYwN.png&h=8dc17faa&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:34:24.000Z","msg":"2013年 《Supper Moment世界變了樣演唱會》opening:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XQM5PE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XQM5PE.jpg&h=efdb38b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">演唱會由宣示對社會不滿的片段打頭陣</span>，舊香港演變到新香港，進而到國教風波、免費電視牌照事件，<span style=\"color: red;\">梁振英的「順得哥情失嫂意」soundbite在starhall再次播出，全場的噓聲</span>，噓得比同樣在片段現身的阿奎諾三世更厲害。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MtmXs22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtmXs22.jpg&h=7761f628&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N16Xs22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN16Xs22.jpg&h=e64b0f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱血、反建制的開場，在一般港式演唱會絕不會看到，這就是青春的本錢。青春，亦體現在歌曲本身，Supper Moment的歌最常用追尋夢想做題材，聽了這麼多年演唱會，或許，聽得最多講夢想的歌就在今晚。<br />\n<br />\n原文: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MusicPicks/photos/a.375030362614551/458219174295669/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMusicPicks%2Fphotos%2Fa.375030362614551%2F458219174295669%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=fb30d5b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MusicPicks/photos/a.375030362614551/458219174295669/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n-------<br />\n2019年<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yNinD9Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyNinD9Q.jpg&h=6dfaac6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g0uqBWw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg0uqBWw.jpg&h=127b6462&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjtiWWx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjtiWWx.jpg&h=86bf8c4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSupper Moment昨晚在會展出席電競音樂節，一連唱了《258km/h》、《一樣不一樣》、《大丈夫》、《幸福之歌》和《說再見了吧》，台下觀眾瞬間變歌迷 ，仿如變了他們的主場騷！<br />\n最後加唱《世界變了樣》<br />\n<br />\n在同一晚<span style=\"color: red;\">會場外</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">警方在干諾道中開槍，疑發射橡膠子彈，以驅散示威者，其後再施放催淚彈，並再舉黑旗。大批手持長盾的防暴警向前推進。</span><br />\n<br />\n活動上Supper Moment最後唱出《世界變了樣》，曲終時，台下有人大叫：「光復香港，時代革命！」但<span style=\"color: red;\">台上各人未有回應便離去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\nBy 金鐘勁flight"},{"pid":"dcb60cf067747a551061e3889d5e8ec6f124b39c","tid":1560251,"uid":80303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T20:01:11.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"8e4d34337b19e3e19975cdaa48482c8bee9c02a3","tid":1560251,"uid":222541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo